high_descs: Turn left, walk towards the middle of the kitchen, and then turn left towards the stove.
Pick up the kettle on the stove.
Walk towards the sink on your right.
Place the kettle in the sink, fill it up with water, and pick it back up.
Turn right, walk towards the lettuce, turn right towards the end of the counter, turn left and walk towards the circle table to your right.
Place the kettle next to the plant on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place the kettle with water on the circle table.

high_descs: Turn left, walk to the stove on the left
Grab the kettle on the stove
Turn right, walk to the sink
Put the kettle in the skin, open the faucet, wash the kettle, close the faucet, take the kettle
Turn right, walk around the counter to the window, turn right, walk to the dining table
Put the kettle down on the dining table
anns.task_desc: Wash the kettle from the stove, move the kettle to the dining table

high_descs: Move to the stove to the left of the sink.
Pick up the tea pot from the stove.
Move to the sink to the right of the stove.
Place the tea pot inside the sink and fill with water before picking the pot back up and turning off the water.
Move to the kitchen table behind you and to the left of the fridge.
Place the tea pot on the round table.
anns.task_desc: Put a filled tea pot on the table.
